02:15:23.010 --> 02:15:23.910
I get it.

1576
02:15:24.690 --> 02:15:25.370
It's a good joke.

1577
02:15:25.890 --> 02:15:26.470
Good joke.

1578
02:15:27.930 --> 02:15:28.510
All right.

1579
02:15:34.350 --> 02:15:35.590
Well... Goodbye.

1580
02:15:37.290 --> 02:15:38.670
No understand word.

1581
02:15:40.310 --> 02:15:41.990
See you later.

1582
02:15:42.410 --> 02:15:43.650
But I won't see you later.

1583
02:15:48.490 --> 02:15:49.330
I know.

1584
02:15:52.430 --> 02:15:54.150
How do you say
goodbye back home?

1585
02:15:55.270 --> 02:15:55.650
We don't.

1586
02:15:57.570 --> 02:15:59.170
We do this.

1587
02:17:50.890 --> 02:17:57.070
Journey to Earth will take four
years. two months. and eleven days.

1588
02:18:36.558 --> 02:18:44.931
Contamined. detected.

1589
02:18:38.241 --> 02:18:40.162
{\an8}<i>Grace</i>

1590
02:18:51.670 --> 02:19:10.170
Contaminant detected.

1591
02:19:13.199 --> 02:19:15.088
{\an8}<i>‫Engines Shutting Down</i>

1592
02:19:20.338 --> 02:19:21.987
{\an8}<i>Depressurization in progress
WARNING</i>

1593
02:19:54.290 --> 02:19:55.290
There's a leak.

1594
02:19:57.910 --> 02:19:58.750
The problem is the xenonite.

1595
02:20:00.190 --> 02:20:01.810
The Taumoeba can get through it.

1596
02:20:02.870 --> 02:20:05.290
Probably because we bred it
in the xenonite breeder tanks

1597
02:20:05.510 --> 02:20:06.790
it evolved to escape it.

1598
02:20:07.810 --> 02:20:10.730
I was able to stop it before it
ate all the astrophage on the ship.

1599
02:20:13.670 --> 02:20:15.210
Rocky's ship is
built of xenonite.

1600
02:20:16.550 --> 02:20:19.070
The Taumoeba will already
be in its fuel lines.

1601
02:20:20.370 --> 02:20:23.070
He won't be able to find the leak
because the leak is the ship itself.

1602
02:20:23.810 --> 02:20:27.150
He'll be without
any fuel. Stranded.

1603
02:20:27.730 --> 02:20:29.630
His life support
systems will fail.

1604
02:20:32.330 --> 02:20:35.090
If that doesn't kill him
the radiation sickness will.

1605
02:20:38.390 --> 02:20:41.770
He's looking at a long. slow.

1606
02:20:43.610 --> 02:20:45.490
painful death.

1607
02:20:48.450 --> 02:20:48.650
Alone.

1608
02:20:59.296 --> 02:21:00.976
{\an8}<i>Who am I?</i>

1609
02:21:05.540 --> 02:21:07.031
<i>Intercept time</i>

1610
02:21:09.335 --> 02:21:10.757
<i>56.187 days</i>

1611
02:21:12.710 --> 02:21:14.030
I can't do both.

1612
02:21:16.190 --> 02:21:17.130
I can go home.

1613
02:21:20.850 --> 02:21:22.170
Or I can save

1614
02:21:41.770 --> 02:21:44.690
I've sent you detailed
logs of all of our findings

1615
02:21:45.390 --> 02:21:48.270
and enough Taumoeba
for you to start

1616
02:21:48.270 --> 02:21:49.830
your very own Taumoeba farm.

1617
02:21:49.712 --> 02:21:51.618
{\an8}<i>‫Ringo</i>

1618
02:21:53.330 --> 02:21:54.570
At least I never
have to hear you say.

1619
02:21:54.830 --> 02:21:56.070
I told you so.

1620
02:21:57.610 --> 02:21:59.030
Even though you were right.

1621
02:22:01.193 --> 02:22:02.006
{\an8}<i>George</i>

1622
02:22:02.031 --> 02:22:02.951
{\an8}<i>‫John</i>

1623
02:22:02.976 --> 02:22:03.928
{\an8}<i>Paul</i>

1624
02:22:03.953 --> 02:22:05.162
{\an8}<i>Ringo</i>

1625
02:25:40.170 --> 02:25:42.490
I'm here. buddy.

1626
02:26:05.170 --> 02:26:09.670
Earth. Rocky. Rocky. Earth.

1627
02:26:09.670 --> 02:26:12.170
Hello. Earth. I am Rocky.

1628
02:26:12.170 --> 02:26:16.770
I am Rocky from Erid. I am not
Rocky from movie. No. no. no. no.

1629
02:26:16.770 --> 02:26:20.090
I'm pretty sure they know that.

1630
02:26:20.170 --> 02:26:24.370
I left you detailed logs of all of our findings.
and I threw in a little something else just for fun.

1631
02:26:27.130 --> 02:26:28.590
Hopefully it all makes sense.

1632
02:26:29.870 --> 02:26:31.910
And if not. you're smart.

1633
02:26:33.610 --> 02:26:34.550
You'll figure it out.

1634
02:26:36.310 --> 02:26:40.030
This is Dr. Captain Ryland
Grace reporting from the Hail Mary.

1635
02:26:40.170 --> 02:26:42.170
As the Eridians say...

1636
02:26:59.170 --> 02:27:00.150
Let's begin.

1637
02:27:15.989 --> 02:27:18.153
<i>‫Peanut Butter</i>

1638
02:27:18.183 --> 02:27:19.762
<i>‫Taumoeba Farm</i>

1639
02:27:52.750 --> 02:27:54.090
Good morning. Armando.

1640
02:27:55.570 --> 02:27:56.610
You shouldn't have.

1641
02:28:03.130 --> 02:28:07.130
That's a noogie. I'm coming!

1642
02:28:12.334 --> 02:28:14.420
Why you take so long?

1643
02:28:14.730 --> 02:28:15.790
Why you always
gotta be so early?

1644
02:28:15.500 --> 02:28:17.500
I knock and I knock.

1645
02:28:17.290 --> 02:28:20.150
Yeah. I know. and I ignored you.

1646
02:28:20.292 --> 02:28:21.167
Grace. the door.

1647
02:28:21.191 --> 02:28:23.191
Close the door.

1648
02:28:24.250 --> 02:28:26.810
Why? I thought this
was a safe neighborhood.

1649
02:28:26.750 --> 02:28:28.334
I make door. You close door.

1650
02:28:28.330 --> 02:28:31.050
Okay. Armando
likes the fresh air.

1651
02:28:44.770 --> 02:28:47.170
Can we talk about the water
temperature a little bit?

1652
02:28:47.084 --> 02:28:48.167
Yes.

1653
02:28:48.090 --> 02:28:51.110
It's amazing just that
you've done it at all.

1654
02:28:52.530 --> 02:28:53.250
Very cold.

1655
02:28:54.170 --> 02:28:55.930
And before it was boiling.

1656
02:28:56.810 --> 02:28:57.690
Is there an in-between?

1657
02:28:58.709 --> 02:29:00.042
I ask Adrian to work on this.

1658
02:29:06.510 --> 02:29:11.290
Please tell the bio-dome
illumination team that it's perfect now.

1659
02:29:11.959 --> 02:29:14.459
You no want it sunnier than this?

1660
02:29:13.890 --> 02:29:17.650
Oh no. this is. you know
I'm a sucker for the fog.

1661
02:29:27.334 --> 02:29:28.417
Grace.

1662
02:29:28.250 --> 02:29:29.650
Yapa.

1663
02:29:30.667 --> 02:29:33.417
Eridian scientists are ready...

1664
02:29:33.459 --> 02:29:35.709
to prepare Hail Mary for journey home.

1665
02:29:43.750 --> 02:29:44.970
Can I think about it?

1666
02:29:46.667 --> 02:29:49.000
Yes. think about it long time.

1667
02:30:35.110 --> 02:30:37.950
Good morning. class.

1668
02:30:38.930 --> 02:30:42.590
Okay. Everyone.
take their seats.

1669
02:30:43.630 --> 02:30:44.910
Let's wake up.

1670
02:30:48.810 --> 02:30:50.350
Who can tell me
the speed of light?

1671
